//  ╭── Row 3: home row (pos 34-45) ──╮
    &sk LSHFT &kp LGUI  &kp LALT  &kp LCTRL &kp LSHFT  &kp LC(C)            &kp LC(INS) &kp LEFT  &kp UP    &kp DOWN  &kp RIGHT &sk RSHFT
//  ╭── Row 4: bottom + inner thumbs (pos 46-63) ──╮
    &kp LC(L) &kp LSHFT XXX       XXX       &kp LC(F)  &kp LC(V)  XXX XXX &kp PSCRN XXX XXX XXX  &kp LS(INS) &kp HOME &kp PG_UP &kp PG_DN &kp END &kp LC(L)
//  ╭── Row 5: outer + main thumbs (pos 64-79) ──╮
    &kp LC(K) &kp LC(Z) &kp LC(Y) &kp LC(LS(G)) &kp LC(G)  XXX XXX &kp LG(D)  XXX XXX XXX  &kp LC(F) &kp LC(LS(G)) &kp LC(G) &kp LC(H) &kp LC(K)
)

